{"tid":1476714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田北俊收黨員投訴信 不滿其支持「反對派黑衣暴徒」","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:34:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":200,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"a36015a69fb2a7b33a2493166bc220767cfc2b7b","tid":1476714,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:00:26.000Z","msg":"自由黨榮譽主席田北俊今日在Facebook上載一封投訴信，由「一眾自由黨區議員、中常委、青年團等人」發出，<span style=\"color: red;\">強烈不滿黨魁鍾國斌及田北俊等人，早前去信林鄭要求撤回修例及成立獨立調查委員會，認為此舉「等同支持一班破壞香港法治的反對派黑衣暴徒」。</span><br />\n<br />\n信中又批評田北俊當年反對23條，令該黨成為「建制派叛徒」，並指若田等人「一意孤行繼續強行粗暴使用自由黨的名字，企圖作出反國家及政府的行為」，將會成立一個「反田北俊、鍾國斌、周梁淑怡、劉健儀的群組」，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求他們下台，甚至聯同其他黨員一同退黨，另立新的商界政黨，就像當年經民聯一樣。</span><br />\n<br />\n有自由黨中人分析，發信者應為黨員，但只是普通黨員，過去未曾代表該黨參選，該人強調「肯定不是由一班人共同提出」，又指黨內核心已就此作討論，相信該投訴信不代表黨內主流意見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSvYqAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSvYqAz.jpg&h=e0fc0159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tienjames/photos/a.578840672157323/2956155071092526/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftienjames%2Fphotos%2Fa.578840672157323%2F2956155071092526%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8e8742dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tienjames/photos/a.578840672157323/2956155071092526/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2427912/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2427912%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8ee50735\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2427912/</a>"},{"pid":"59514c315fb5c43769be8fec8191492457c08f5a","tid":1476714,"uid":212626,"like":301,"dislike":1,"score":300,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"由於信中下款沒有標明誰人寫，田北俊在Facebook說「夠薑開名」，又諷刺「請信中各位所謂的聯署黨員開名，如果唔係，好難去中聯辦領功」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb5d70d506433169154065ca9cc07de61b4cbbe","tid":1476714,"uid":79046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:01:35.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅大好機會！！十八區we connect，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823人鏈823人鏈823人鏈</span></span></strong>，百萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"b6cfa42e1ce765d1350430c05983612a654392b3","tid":1476714,"uid":46966,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />田少串過馬撚"},{"pid":"0b759003342d4dbe0dd42590f2cca79f92323942","tid":1476714,"uid":212626,"like":334,"dislike":0,"score":334,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oH8i93U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoH8i93U.png&h=b2c485df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民賤聯中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38c4c3ee55e8aebb2258778d6d34bb081cc2ef3","tid":1476714,"uid":164730,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:03:47.000Z","msg":"自由黨跟本就係靠田北俊、周梁淑怡、劉健儀呢幾個養 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab87e03dccca17f3ce8fb5ae94baae07be8dbed","tid":1476714,"uid":172627,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"無名你話你係共產黨都得嫁啦"},{"pid":"bf59744a4c1ea5e2b49bd1c923305c299c29a4bf","tid":1476714,"uid":304321,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":