普通黨員，過去未曾代表該黨參選，該人強調「肯定不是由一班人共同提出」，又指黨內核心已就此作討論，相信該投訴信不代表黨內主流意見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSvYqAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSvYqAz.jpg&h=e0fc0159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tienjames/photos/a.578840672157323/2956155071092526/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftienjames%2Fphotos%2Fa.578840672157323%2F2956155071092526%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8e8742dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tienjames/photos/a.578840672157323/2956155071092526/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2427912/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2427912%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8ee50735\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2427912/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c945c7fb4bc589d8c8f95be8ed8d505f0ddd7c90","tid":1476714,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"896448ac5c51530097db42ecfd1293969a6ca854","tid":1476714,"uid":256059,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:13:01.000Z","msg":"最尾警告好似恐嚇信咁，黨內事務又聲稱有大部分支持，洗乜又瓷器又缸瓦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"真係大部分支持佢地一早迫左宮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c75fa280913fd3170e15832a1698d69ca863fc4","tid":1476714,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" clas